      <abstract>
        <p>New York Knick center Patrick Ewing has arthroscopic surgery on left knee (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Patrick Ewing of the Knicks underwent arthroscopic surgery to clean out his left knee yesterday. Dr. Norman Scott, who performed the operation at Manhattan's Beth Israel Hospital, called the surgery on the 37-year-old center a success.</p>
